HEADWORD: Immix
<hw>Im*mix"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>in-</ets> in + <ets>mix</ets>.]</ety> <def>To mix; to mingle.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Amongst her tears <qex>immixing</qex> prayers meek.</q>
<rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Immixable</ent>⟦br⟧
